*Rođaka* je posetila našu kuću. (My relative visited our house.)
Sestra mi je jedina *rođaka*. (My sister is my only relative.)
Bio je na proslavi kod svoje *rođake*. (He was at a celebration with his relative.)
Nadam se da će moja *rođaka* biti zdrava. (I hope my relative will be healthy.)
Njegova *rođaka* je bila na venčanju. (His relative was at the wedding.)